latestPosts.caption: 🫶🏻 Thank you to all that have shown empathy and support to our Hispanic community. For the time being I cannot bring myself to post regular content while families are hurting, these people don’t need my outfit of the day, they need my prayers and my support. If all you can do is take time to pray today, then that’s more then enough 🫶🏻 just PLEASE don’t spread hate, immigration aside, if your family was hurting in any way you’d want the same kindness and compassion.
latestPosts.alt: Photo by The Other Jessica on June 11, 2025. May be an image of macrame and text that says 'Please be grateful, I cannot enjoy my food knowing that our people are in detention centers Hungry! Scared! Cold! Sick! ALONE! I realized I'm more blessed than I ever acknowledged and it's heartbreaking.'.
